title: Production of Wheat flour in Canada 2016
summary: The graph illustrates the Production of Wheat in Canada the year 2016 .
The Production is very low in the first third of the year , before it rises sharply until October , reaching a maximum of 20000 Tonnes .
Then the Production decreased again for the remaining months of the year .
gold: This figure shows the Canadian production of wheat flour of 2016 . Production is measured in tonnes . Production is the lowest during the month of January at approximately 19500 .
